news.title: Four SEZs to come up off Yamuna Expressway near Agra
news.para: The YEIDA board, during a meeting on Monday, approved the project within a one-and-a-half km radius on both sides of the Yamuna Expressway near Agra. A consultant, said officials, has been directed to submit a master plan within the next two months.

news.title: Tamil Nadu: Three-floor buildings with eight houses don't need final certificate
news.para: At present, completion certificate is not necessary for residential buildings up to 12m in height and not exceeding three dwelling units.

news.title: RR Kabel posts net profit of Rs 70.95 crore in Q3 FY24
news.para: RR Kabel's net consolidated total income and gains stood at Rs 1,645.76 crore in Q3 FY24, a growth of 10.96 per cent from Rs 1,483.25 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Haryana: 100 illegal colonies on 500 acres razed, DTCP will now recover cost
news.para: In the last six months, the department carried out 70 demolition drives in which more than 100 illegal colonies — spread over 500 acres — were razed costing lakhs of rupees.

news.title: Ahmedabad civic body gets Rs 3.20 lakh per sq metre for plot opposite Rajpath Club
news.para: This coveted Ahmedabad Municipal Corporation (AMC) plot, just opposite Rajpath Club, shattered records, fetching the AMC a staggering Rs 3.20 lakh per square metre, the highest price ever for any civic body-owned land parcel.

news.title: Bankruptcy court approves J Kumar Infraprojects' bid for Pranav Construction
news.para: As part of the insolvency process, J Kumar Infraprojects has proposed to pay Rs 45 crore for the acquisition of the real estate firm against its admitted liabilities of about Rs 212 crore.

news.title: Nuvoco Vistas Corporation posts profit of Rs 31.03 crore in Q3 FY24
news.para: Nuvoco Vistas Corporation's net consolidated total income and gains stood at Rs 2,431.87 crore in Q3 FY24, a dip of 6.78 per cent from Rs 2,608.76 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Kochi: Housing project under Rajiv Awas Yojana faces vigilance probe
news.para: The overall cost of a 300sqft unit in the apartment complex comes to Rs 19.5 lakh under the project, whereas, under Life Mission, the cost of construction for a 500sqft residential unit will be around Rs 4 lakh.

news.title: Mindspace Business Parks REIT's net profit up 16.05% in Q3 FY24
news.para: Mindspace REIT's net operating income (NOI) grew by 10.4% year-on-year in Q3 FY24 to Rs 473 crore. It recorded NOI of Rs 1,419 crore for the nine month period in FY24, registering a 12.8% growth year-on-year.

news.title: Reports on illegal buildings being doctored: Candolim villagers
news.para: A resident of the village, Anthony D’Souza, said that following a complaint made by him about an illegal structure in the CRZ area at Dando, the Candolim panchayat had recently conducted a site inspection.

news.title: Mangaluru civic body decides to buy land for housing schemes through TDR
news.para: Many applications for homes are pending with the Mangaluru corporation due to shortage of government land to implement housing projects. As a result, beneficiaries are yet to be sanctioned sites in the city limits.With the Mangaluru City Corporation (MCC) facing the issue of non-availability of land to implement housing projects.

news.title: Holcim eyes $30 billion valuation with its North American business listing
news.para: In the biggest shake-up at Holcim since the Swiss company took over French rival Lafarge in 2015, the divestment will likely be completed in the first half of 2025. The spin-off could value the new company at around $30 billion, Jenisch told reporters, with Holcim retaining no stake.

news.title: Home prices in Hong Kong drop 6.8% in 2023, outlook still weak
news.para: Home prices in one of the world's most expensive property markets dropped 1.4% in December from the previous month, official data showed on Monday, following a revised 1.9% fall in November.

news.title: Lucknow administration forms five teams to find eligible PMAY beneficiaries
news.para: Each team comprises officials from LMC, LDA, Revenue Department, and District Urban Development Agency (DUDA). The teams have been tasked with conducting a comprehensive survey of the Akbarnagar area and the residents who are to be rehabilitated.

news.title: Delhi: MCD prohibits use of MLALAD funds for development works in unauthorised colonies, housing societies
news.para: In an order dated January 24, the civic body directed that no development works in unauthorised colonies and co-operative housing societies will be carried out using the MLALAD funds.

news.title: Greater Noida development body will pay Noida authority Rs 10 crore per month to clear dues
news.para: The Authority had borrowed Rs 2,900 crore to disburse the 64.7% additional compensation to farmers from whom lands were acquired for various development projects. From April, Greater Noida has decided to pay a monthly instalment of Rs 10 crore to the Noida Authority, officials said.

news.title: Reliance Home Finance headed for voluntary liquidation, surrenders CoR
news.para: Authum Investment and Infrastructure Ltd, which acquired the stock exchange-listed Reliance Home Finance a year ago, has proposed voluntary liquidation of the company.

news.title: Shri Ram Multicom to acquire Sarga Hotels under IBC
news.para: The Kolkata bench of the National Company Law Tribunal approved a Rs 301 crore resolution plan against Rs 816 crore admitted claims from creditors, employees, and trade creditors.

news.title: China Evergrande ordered to liquidate, owing $300 billion
news.para: Evergrande, the world's most indebted developer with more than $300 billion of total liabilities, sent a struggling property sector into a tailspin when it defaulted on its debt in 2021.

news.title: Pune-based Ashdan Properties' bid tops eight offers for debt of Rolta India
news.para: Ashdan's bid beat eight other bidders including data centre company Cyfuture India and Jai Corp vice chairman Virendra Jain among others after creditors scrutinised the value of bids received.
